tspan.tspan: And had a lot of impact:

text.tspan: A RAND Corporation study estimated that a
successful BDS campaign against Israel could cost
the Israeli economy a cumulative $47 billion over ten
years and there was a 46% drop in foreign direct
investment into Israel in 2014 compared to 2013. [3]
Even just the drop of Veolia from public constracts
were worth at least 20 billion USD. [5]
